cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video segmentation. It also involves statistical techniques (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) for clustering and concept drift detection. Information retrieval (cs.IR) could also be a possible sub-category as the paper deals with organizing and categorizing video data. Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques (cs.SD) for energy minimization.
